message.body: Hello stranger!
Hey! How are you?
Good! No long no talk hahah! About to start Christmas shopping. You?!
I know.... I was actually on a cruise last week so I wasn't here. Just starting ehh? I started Sunday night when I got back. Lol.
What??? You went on a cruise! No wonder, I texted you. Where'd you go?
What did you text me?
Jamaica, Grand Cayman and Mexico.
Yes, I don't exactly have the longest list in the world. And my family is hard to shop for.
Hahahahahah wow, figured that'd be something you would have mentioned! Jeez Steve...
Hahah I was just saying hi. Nothing major.
Lol I'm sorry. Got so busy with making sure that I had all my work done and packing before I left, I didn't really get to tell anyone.
Did you have fun??? How was the weather?

It was fun. The boat was full of activities and shows so I enjoyed that. Huge boat. The weather wasn't too great, rained all day at Jamaica so we didn't get to get off the boat. Drizzles here and there at Grand Cayman and Mexico, but got to go to the beach and played with dolphins!
Awwww dolphins! I want to do that one day. Did you go with Carnival?
Nah, Norwegian Cruise Line.
Oh cool. Was it for a week?
Yeah. Got back Sunday night.
ï¿¼
Look at the little men! Lol.
I know!!! We took them to get their Christmas pictures taken. It wad so cute.
Which ones which?
Guess!
Ethan on the left?
Wow, you are good!
Haha. I think I can tell them apart now. And I haven't even met them!
Impressive. I even get stumped sometimes!
I am at the mall right now and it's crazy.
Lines everywhere!!!!
I literally just finished my Christmas shopping...walking out now.
Very efficient. Done in one day? Lol.
